Title: Designates a portion of the state highway system as the "Jake Acara Worker's Memorial Highway"
Summary: Designates a portion of the state highway system in the town of Yorktown, county of Westchester, as the "Jake Acara Worker's Memorial Highway".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "Jake Acara Worker's Memorial Highway"
